{"tid":1556682,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"徹底打臉! 美國同性戀治療中心創辦人「出櫃」","createTime":"2019-09-09T23:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T05:23:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de170c02518b7903bc596cfde146e4f42115dd64","tid":1556682,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/201909/201909051973804_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F201909%2F201909051973804_l.jpg&h=d042e727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國南卡羅來納州同性戀治療中心「Hope for Wholeness」創辦人蓋姆(McKrae Game)，今年夏天公開「出櫃」，並且對曾被他治療過的人道歉。<br />\n<br />\n創辦人公開出櫃 對曾治療過的人道歉<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，51歲的蓋姆上周接受《The Post and Courier》訪問時表示，「轉換性向治療(Conversion therapy)」不僅是一個謊言，還非常有害，他的餘生都會對被他治療過的人感到歉意。蓋姆的出櫃距離他被同性戀治療中心的董事會解雇已將近兩年，之前他一直努力宣導利用宗教信仰力量來改變性向，但他承認在這種信念中受到嚴重心理傷害。<br />\n<br />\n直言「治療同性戀」是謊言 嘗試融入同志社區<br />\n<br />\n蓋姆表示：「治療同性戀不僅是一個謊言，而且對人的心理是非常有害。因為它只是一種虛假的宣傳」，他目前正試圖融入在20年前全力抨擊的同志社區，同時譴責試圖改變同志性向的行為。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，目前全美國有18個州以及華盛頓特區禁止對未成年人進行「性向轉換治療」，不過南卡羅來納州並非是其中之一。"},{"pid":"3497653f274a68aa515dc2e0823a85e45d43d935","tid":1556682,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:46:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/international/201909/201909051973804.html?fbclid=IwAR0iCWSwC0HZdhPt5LWjecj1aDMIjctuhFETUNVKy_V12DDL8OSI_xarG38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Finternational%2F201909%2F201909051973804.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0iCWSwC0HZdhPt5LWjecj1aDMIjctuhFETUNVKy_V12DDL8OSI_xarG38&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=b35b23cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/international/201909/201909051973804.html?fbclid=IwAR0iCWSwC0HZdhPt5LWjecj1aDMIjctuhFETUNVKy_V12DDL8OSI_xarG38</a>"},{"pid":"395e9d9f5f6726b9c8bd6e7c7e32bcc92977e3ee","tid":1556682,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci